<!DOCTYPE html>
 <html lang="en">
  <head>
   <meta charset="utf-8"/>
   <title>
    Inactive url
   </title>
   <style type="text/css">
    html, body{
     font-family: sans-serif;
     line-height: 160%;
     font-size: 14px;
     margin: 0;
     height: 0;
     padding: 0;
     margin: 0;
     background-color: #fafafa;
     width: 100%;
     height: 100%;
   }
   p{
     margin: 0;
     margin-top: 5px;
     margin-bottom: 5px;
   }
   table{
     width: 100%;
     height: 100%;
   }
   table td{
     vertical-align: center;
   }
   .fixed-footer{
     position: fixed;
     bottom: 0;
     left:0;
     right:0;
     color:#474747;
   }
   .container{
     width: 600px;
     margin: 0 auto;
     background-color: #fff;
     border: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
     box-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
   }
   .logo-wrapper{
     display: block;
     height: 50px;
     width: 166px;
     background-position: 4px center;
     background-repeat: no-repeat;
     padding: 0;
   }
   </style>
  </head>
  <body>
   <table align="center">
    <tr>
     <td>
      <div class="container">
       <header>
        <div class="logo-wrapper" style="background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,')">
        </div>
       </header>
       <div style="padding-left: 10px; padding-right:10px;">
        <p>
         This is an inactive url, please see
         <a href="http://www.wolterskluwer.be">
          http://www.wolterskluwer.be
         </a>
        </p>
       </div>
       <footer>
       </footer>
      </div>
     </td>
    </tr>
   </table>
   <!-- <div class="fixed-footer">
   <marquee>kijk een marquee!</marquee>
 </div> -->
  </body>
 </html>
